Package cycleguard.database.accessor

Class UserProfileAccessor.UserProfile

java.lang.Object
cycleguard.database.AbstractDatabaseEntry
cycleguard.database.AbstractDatabaseUserEntry
cycleguard.database.accessor.UserProfileAccessor.UserProfile
Enclosing class:
UserProfileAccessor
public static final class UserProfileAccessor.UserProfile extends AbstractDatabaseUserEntry
DynamoDbBean linking a username to that user's profile information.
  • displayName - Custom display name of user: not necessarily username
  • bio - Custom biography/description of user
  • pack - User's current pack. getBlankEntry sets pack to empty string, but defaults to null.
  • isPublic - If the user's profile is publicly viewable.
  • isNewAccount - If the account is new and should display a tutorial on startup.
  • profileIcon - Name of profile icon used by user.
